This topic explains how to install Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) on Microsoft Azure manually.

To install PCF on Azure manually, do the following:

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure Manually](../om/azure/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure Manually](../om/azure/config-manual.html).

1. Deploy PAS. See [Deploying PAS on Azure](./azure-er-config.html).
